Mental health initiatives

1 Public awareness and education - 
educational materials : develop and distribute informtive materials on mental health topics to schools, workplaces, and communities.

2 Access to information and resources - 
Online resources - create and maintain online platforms with reliable information, self-help resources and tools for mental health management.

3 Training and workshop - 
Mental health first aid : provide training programs, such as mental health first aid, to educate individuals on recognizing signs of mental health issues and offering initial support.
